  * [Feature] KBL: intel_rapl driver support (LP: #1591640)
    - powercap/intel_rapl: Add support for Kabylake
  * Xenial update to v4.4.61 stable release (LP: #1682140)
    - drm/vmwgfx: Type-check lookups of fence objects
