linux-raspi2 (4.4.0-1034.41) xenial; urgency=low

  * CVE-2016-8655 (LP: #1646318)
      - packet: fix race condition in packet_set_ring

 -- Brad Figg <brad.figg@canonical.com>  Fri, 02 Dec 2016 10:01:26 -0800

